line_2: And to his utmost power the Throne preserv'd,

line_1: Well then, Things handsomly were serv'd:
line_2: My Mistress for the Strangers carv'd.

line_1: Each day a sister lamb is serv'd,
line_2: And at the glutton's table carv'd;

line_1: Yet well this little page his lord had served,
line_2: His watchful eye from many a snare preserved,

line_1: This Cock the Eagle's fire had served,
line_2: And of the son had much deserved;
